Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.65,PW,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80}京都大支柱  第24层
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.65,PW4,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fsp-1\pos(611,555)}Core  Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,720)}无论如何都要阻止废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何都要得到安可儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  你不骂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在连生气的时间都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  是不是不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走这么远一个人都没遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都被军方带走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们平安就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这门后面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们没去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可不存在玩忽职守的半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又发生异常震动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到什么方法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我带了一张超级王牌过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,超兴奋  太棒了太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次见到这么棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:05.88,title,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fad(0,350)\pos(402,590)}虚数运动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:05.88,title,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fscx80\fad(0,350)\pos(402,540)}Imaginary Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,太美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如此漂亮  诱人  激动人心的百分百完美装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是出自谁手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}真是太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,直人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为现在不是在意这种事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  快教训一下这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这种老得要发霉的古董
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然能得到比我还高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我无法认同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你在意的也不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,您把我全身上下都看遍后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,夸我真漂亮  夸我最棒的那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都是骗我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这里的齿轮也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是齿轮您全喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹的齿轮才是世上最美的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38)}我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,您是要我脱给您看对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是  我没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}不能脱  不能脱啊  琉兹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个笨蛋给我适可而止好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你来这是要干什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个少年  把Initial-Y系列…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我给大家重新介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他是见浦直人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,各位或许有很多疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要修理大支柱必须借助他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉他们的视线好刺人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,正如各位所见他是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不过也是现在必不可少的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,离废弃还剩3小时57分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先放下对这位少年的质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,听从玛丽师傅的吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请交给我保管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,第一处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第二处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第三处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,直人大人  您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有18处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比预料中要少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,运作异常的地方有4047处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过跟重力异常有关的只有18处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有18处的话应该来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我具体在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不懂这种图啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说个大概就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽师傅  请指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,LV3以下的故障
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,共12处由肯拉德师傅带各位去处理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,时间紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,无需拆卸检修直接动手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔塔带上工具跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是故障部件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,连图都看不懂的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我这修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我这也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我这也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我这也修完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一处在人类进不去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹  请你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能对我下令的只有直人大…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  琉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,从你所在的地方跳起52.3米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,转向水平视线上移47.5度的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再跳14.25米垂直降落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有个直径0.7微米的齿轮松了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要在不阻碍它运转的前提下修好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不甘心  但也只有你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这是把我当机器对待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是精密仪器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会小心管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽  就是那边的机芯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,从右边数起第四个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不过不搭个落脚的架子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间搭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你就看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  去下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我家的小公主很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在她的小脑袋里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,塞着过去发生过的所有故障及其修理方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能参照脑里的大量资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,瞬间找出最快最好的处理方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是玛丽・贝尔・布雷洁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她跟你一样  都是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,全部修完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第24层  气压控制区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗常数  正常值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不协和音程  听不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,观测班班长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,检测项目  全部通过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,修理工作全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然真成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是在做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的  真成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我为之前怀疑你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是你的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可我也没帮什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谦虚什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要是找不出故障在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,根本谈不上修理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们花了这么多天都没完成的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮上你们的忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是你拯救了两千万人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,废弃开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,720)}解除连接轴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.33,PW2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fsp5\fad(0,350)}京都『军队』司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,720)}第52939号轴  分离完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧开始废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不能留下任何证据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给我快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,废弃就是利用重力控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让这城市坠落到星球内部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,若要阻止废弃的话  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,得直接干涉系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要把军方的恶行公诸于众
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这也只会让市民陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想想别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有  有没有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,您怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不  30分钟就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能阻止城市继续下坠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,用虚数运动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要阻止城市下坠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,必须生成反重力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而唯一能做到这点的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是倒转能量输出的虚数运动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我牺牲琉兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只是暂时借用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,又保证不了能装回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我  我一定会帮你修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  没商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,主人  以我「侍从者」之名发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,无论陷入什么样的险境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我都可以救您逃出生天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  愚蠢的直人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,您没愚蠢到牺牲了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还能向我露出笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹没必要做出牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,直人大人  一定能修好我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,废弃  进入最终进程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,生成重力能量  倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开始倒计
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,5  4  3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,实施废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,实施废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,城市下陷50  100  150
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,重力…反转了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在把城市推上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快  重新编写系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,720)}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.83,PW,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fsp5\fad(0,350)}京都大支柱  第24层  重力控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.83,PW4,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fsp-1\pos(460,555)\fad(0,350)}Core  Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能争取30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再勉强的话虚数运动装置会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有30分钟就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多声音在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是以前听到过的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是谁在阻止废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,统统杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真会挑时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要争取时间对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还是这种工作比较适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我也帮个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这边比较有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这排场好  都不用瞄准了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  那么就敲响开幕的钟声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请放心  稍后我会修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,呵  老爷子好性情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,直人  直人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神  直人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要拯救一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  对  你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让第5个圆筒向右转34度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我方的控制权限被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽  还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽师傅  成功接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,直人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要沉睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕经过了1800926小时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的愚钝依然停留在跳蚤的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过是再睡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我的心比上次还要痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这次跟上次有一点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您这副本来就不好看的尊容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哭丧起来就更惨不忍睹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,直人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  应该说是理所当然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正如构成我的4兆2706亿8643个齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在一丝差错一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  才会有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道这么一个说法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,命运的齿轮
